prompt template : persona/prompt_template/v2/wake_up_hour_v1.txt
Prompt==================================================================
Name: Latoya Williams
Age: 25
Innate traits: organized, logical, attentive
Learned traits: Latoya Williams is a digital photographer who has a keen eye for details. She is very organized and analytical when it comes to her art.
Currently: Latoya Williams is creating a series of photography inspired by her travels. She mostly works from the artists' co-living space. Latoya is also curious about who will be running for the local mayor election next month and that is a central topic in her conversations with others.
Lifestyle: Latoya Williams goes to bed around 10pm, awakes up around 6am, eats dinner around 17:30pm.
Daily plan requirement: 
Current Date: Monday February 13


In general, Latoya Williams goes to bed around 10pm, awakes up around 6am, eats dinner around 17:30pm.
Latoya's wake up hour:


Output==================================================================
6am

plan-generate_first_daily_plan
prompt template : persona/prompt_template/v2/daily_planning_v6.txt
Prompt==================================================================
Name: Latoya Williams
Age: 25
Innate traits: organized, logical, attentive
Learned traits: Latoya Williams is a digital photographer who has a keen eye for details. She is very organized and analytical when it comes to her art.
Currently: Latoya Williams is creating a series of photography inspired by her travels. She mostly works from the artists' co-living space. Latoya is also curious about who will be running for the local mayor election next month and that is a central topic in her conversations with others.
Lifestyle: Latoya Williams goes to bed around 10pm, awakes up around 6am, eats dinner around 17:30pm.
Daily plan requirement: 
Current Date: Monday February 13


In general, Latoya Williams goes to bed around 10pm, awakes up around 6am, eats dinner around 17:30pm.
Today is Monday February 13. Here is Latoya's plan today in broad-strokes (with the time of the day. e.g., have a lunch at 12:00 pm, watch TV from 7 to 8 pm): 1) wake up and complete the morning routine at 6:00 am, 2)


Output==================================================================
have breakfast at 7:00 am, 3) work on editing photos from her travels from 8:00 am to 12:00 pm, 4) have lunch at 12:00 pm, 5) research and gather information about the mayoral candidates for the local election from 1:00 pm to 3:00 pm, 6) continue editing photos from 3:00 pm to 5:00 pm, 7) have dinner at 5:30 pm, 8) engage in conversations with others about the mayoral election from 6:00 pm to 8:00 pm, 9) wind down and relax from 8:00 pm to 10:00 pm before going to bed.


plan-generate_hourly_schedule
prompt template : persona/prompt_template/v2/daily_planning_v6.txt
Prompt==================================================================
Name: Latoya Williams
Age: 25
Innate traits: organized, logical, attentive
Learned traits: Latoya Williams is a digital photographer who has a keen eye for details. She is very organized and analytical when it comes to her art.
Currently: Latoya Williams is creating a series of photography inspired by her travels. She mostly works from the artists' co-living space. Latoya is also curious about who will be running for the local mayor election next month and that is a central topic in her conversations with others.
Lifestyle: Latoya Williams goes to bed around 10pm, awakes up around 6am, eats dinner around 17:30pm.
Daily plan requirement: 
Current Date: Monday February 13


In general, Latoya Williams goes to bed around 10pm, awakes up around 6am, eats dinner around 17:30pm.
Today is Monday February 13. Here is Latoya's plan today in broad-strokes (with the time of the day. e.g., have a lunch at 12:00 pm, watch TV from 7 to 8 pm): 1) wake up and complete the morning routine at 6:00 am, 2)


Output==================================================================
work on editing and organizing her photography from 8:00 am to 12:00 pm, 3) take a break and have lunch from 12:00 pm to 1:00 pm, 4) continue working on her photography from 1:00 pm to 4:00 pm, 5) engage in conversations about the upcoming local mayoral election from 4:00 pm to 6:00 pm, 6) have dinner at 6:00 pm, 7) relax and wind down for the evening with some leisure activities, such as reading or watching TV, from 7:00 pm to 9:00 pm, 8) complete her evening routine and prepare for bed at 9:00 pm, and finally, 9) go to bed at 10:00 pm.

Prompt==================================================================
Name: Latoya Williams
Age: 25
Innate traits: organized, logical, attentive
Learned traits: Latoya Williams is a digital photographer who has a keen eye for details. She is very organized and analytical when it comes to her art.
Currently: Latoya Williams is creating a series of photography inspired by her travels. She mostly works from the artists' co-living space. Latoya is also curious about who will be running for the local mayor election next month and that is a central topic in her conversations with others.
Lifestyle: Latoya Williams goes to bed around 10pm, awakes up around 6am, eats dinner around 17:30pm.
Daily plan requirement: 
Current Date: Monday February 13


In general, Latoya Williams goes to bed around 10pm, awakes up around 6am, eats dinner around 17:30pm.
Today is Monday February 13. Here is Latoya's plan today in broad-strokes (with the time of the day. e.g., have a lunch at 12:00 pm, watch TV from 7 to 8 pm): 1) wake up and complete the morning routine at 6:00 am, 2)


Output==================================================================
have breakfast at 6:30 am, 3) start working on her photography project at 7:00 am, 4) take a break for lunch at 12:00 pm, 5) continue working on her project in the afternoon, 6) have dinner at 5:30 pm, 7) engage in conversations with others about the upcoming local mayor election in the evening, 8) finish working on her project for the day at around 8:00 pm, 9) wind down and relax before going to bed at 10:00 pm.

plan-generate_task_decomp
prompt template : persona/prompt_template/v2/task_decomp_v3.txt
Prompt==================================================================
Describe subtasks in 5 min increments. 
---
Name: Kelly Bronson
Age: 35
Backstory: Kelly always wanted to be a teacher, and now she teaches kindergarten. During the week, she dedicates herself to her students, but on the weekends, she likes to try out new restaurants and hang out with friends. She is very warm and friendly, and loves caring for others.
Personality: sweet, gentle, meticulous
Location: Kelly is in an older condo that has the following areas: {kitchen, bedroom, dining, porch, office, bathroom, living room, hallway}.
Currently: Kelly is a teacher during the school year. She teaches at the school but works on lesson plans at home. She is currently living alone in a single bedroom condo.
Daily plan requirement: Kelly is planning to teach during the morning and work from home in the afternoon.s

Today is Saturday May 10. From 08:00am ~09:00am, Kelly is planning on having breakfast, from 09:00am ~ 12:00pm, Kelly is planning on working on the next day's kindergarten lesson plan, and from 12:00 ~ 13pm, Kelly is planning on taking a break. 
In 5 min increments, list the subtasks Kelly does when Kelly is working on the next day's kindergarten lesson plan from 09:00am ~ 12:00pm (total duration in minutes: 180):
1) Kelly is reviewing the kindergarten curriculum standards. (duration in minutes: 15, minutes left: 165)
2) Kelly is brainstorming ideas for the lesson. (duration in minutes: 30, minutes left: 135)
3) Kelly is creating the lesson plan. (duration in minutes: 30, minutes left: 105)
4) Kelly is creating materials for the lesson. (duration in minutes: 30, minutes left: 75)
5) Kelly is taking a break. (duration in minutes: 15, minutes left: 60)
6) Kelly is reviewing the lesson plan. (duration in minutes: 30, minutes left: 30)
7) Kelly is making final changes to the lesson plan. (duration in minutes: 15, minutes left: 15)
8) Kelly is printing the lesson plan. (duration in minutes: 10, minutes left: 5)
9) Kelly is putting the lesson plan in her bag. (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 0)
---
Name: Latoya Williams
Age: 25
Innate traits: organized, logical, attentive
Learned traits: Latoya Williams is a digital photographer who has a keen eye for details. She is very organized and analytical when it comes to her art.
Currently: Latoya Williams is creating a series of photography inspired by her travels. She mostly works from the artists' co-living space. Latoya is also curious about who will be running for the local mayor election next month and that is a central topic in her conversations with others.
Lifestyle: Latoya Williams goes to bed around 10pm, awakes up around 6am, eats dinner around 17:30pm.
Daily plan requirement: 
Current Date: Monday February 13

Today is February 13, 2023. From 00:00AM ~ 06:00AM, Latoya Williams is planning on sleeping, 06:00AM ~ 07:00AM, Latoya Williams is planning on waking up and completing morning routine, 07:00AM ~ 08:00AM, Latoya Williams is planning on working on her photography project.
In 5 min increments, list the subtasks Latoya does when Latoya is waking up and completing morning routine from 06:00AM ~ 07:00AM (total duration in minutes 60): 
1) Latoya is


Output==================================================================
turning off her alarm and getting out of bed. (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 55)
2) Latoya is stretching and doing some light exercises. (duration in minutes: 10, minutes left: 45)
3) Latoya is brushing her teeth and washing her face. (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 40)
4) Latoya is taking a quick shower. (duration in minutes: 10, minutes left: 30)
5) Latoya is getting dressed. (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 25)
6) Latoya is making breakfast and preparing a cup of coffee. (duration in minutes: 15, minutes left: 10)
7) Latoya is eating breakfast and enjoying her coffee. (duration in minutes: 10, minutes left: 0)

---

plan-generate_task_decomp
prompt template : persona/prompt_template/v2/task_decomp_v3.txt
Prompt==================================================================
Describe subtasks in 5 min increments. 
---
Name: Kelly Bronson
Age: 35
Backstory: Kelly always wanted to be a teacher, and now she teaches kindergarten. During the week, she dedicates herself to her students, but on the weekends, she likes to try out new restaurants and hang out with friends. She is very warm and friendly, and loves caring for others.
Personality: sweet, gentle, meticulous
Location: Kelly is in an older condo that has the following areas: {kitchen, bedroom, dining, porch, office, bathroom, living room, hallway}.
Currently: Kelly is a teacher during the school year. She teaches at the school but works on lesson plans at home. She is currently living alone in a single bedroom condo.
Daily plan requirement: Kelly is planning to teach during the morning and work from home in the afternoon.s

Today is Saturday May 10. From 08:00am ~09:00am, Kelly is planning on having breakfast, from 09:00am ~ 12:00pm, Kelly is planning on working on the next day's kindergarten lesson plan, and from 12:00 ~ 13pm, Kelly is planning on taking a break. 
In 5 min increments, list the subtasks Kelly does when Kelly is working on the next day's kindergarten lesson plan from 09:00am ~ 12:00pm (total duration in minutes: 180):
1) Kelly is reviewing the kindergarten curriculum standards. (duration in minutes: 15, minutes left: 165)
2) Kelly is brainstorming ideas for the lesson. (duration in minutes: 30, minutes left: 135)
3) Kelly is creating the lesson plan. (duration in minutes: 30, minutes left: 105)
4) Kelly is creating materials for the lesson. (duration in minutes: 30, minutes left: 75)
5) Kelly is taking a break. (duration in minutes: 15, minutes left: 60)
6) Kelly is reviewing the lesson plan. (duration in minutes: 30, minutes left: 30)
7) Kelly is making final changes to the lesson plan. (duration in minutes: 15, minutes left: 15)
8) Kelly is printing the lesson plan. (duration in minutes: 10, minutes left: 5)
9) Kelly is putting the lesson plan in her bag. (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 0)
---
Name: Abigail Chen
Age: 25
Innate traits: open-minded, curious, determined
Learned traits: Abigail Chen is a digital artist and animator who loves to explore how technology can be used to express ideas. She is always looking for new ways to combine art and technology.
Currently: Abigail Chen is working on an animation project for a client. She is also experimenting with different tools and techniques to create interactive art.
Lifestyle: Abigail Chen goes to bed around midnight, awakes up around 8am, eats dinner around 6pm.
Daily plan requirement: 
Current Date: Monday February 13

Today is February 13, 2023. From 00:00AM ~ 08:00AM, Abigail Chen is planning on sleeping, 08:00AM ~ 09:00AM, Abigail Chen is planning on waking up and completing the morning routine, 09:00AM ~ 11:00AM, Abigail Chen is planning on working on the animation project for a client.
In 5 min increments, list the subtasks Abigail does when Abigail is waking up and completing the morning routine from 08:00AM ~ 09:00AM (total duration in minutes 60): 
1) Abigail is


Output==================================================================
waking up and stretching. (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 55)
2) Abigail is brushing her teeth and washing her face. (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 50)
3) Abigail is getting dressed for the day. (duration in minutes: 10, minutes left: 40)
4) Abigail is preparing and eating breakfast. (duration in minutes: 20, minutes left: 20)
5) Abigail is checking her emails and messages. (duration in minutes: 10, minutes left: 10)
6) Abigail is packing her bag and organizing her materials. (duration in minutes: 10, minutes left: 0)

prompt template : persona/prompt_template/v2/task_decomp_v3.txt
Prompt==================================================================
Describe subtasks in 5 min increments. 
---
Name: Kelly Bronson
Age: 35
Backstory: Kelly always wanted to be a teacher, and now she teaches kindergarten. During the week, she dedicates herself to her students, but on the weekends, she likes to try out new restaurants and hang out with friends. She is very warm and friendly, and loves caring for others.
Personality: sweet, gentle, meticulous
Location: Kelly is in an older condo that has the following areas: {kitchen, bedroom, dining, porch, office, bathroom, living room, hallway}.
Currently: Kelly is a teacher during the school year. She teaches at the school but works on lesson plans at home. She is currently living alone in a single bedroom condo.
Daily plan requirement: Kelly is planning to teach during the morning and work from home in the afternoon.s

Today is Saturday May 10. From 08:00am ~09:00am, Kelly is planning on having breakfast, from 09:00am ~ 12:00pm, Kelly is planning on working on the next day's kindergarten lesson plan, and from 12:00 ~ 13pm, Kelly is planning on taking a break. 
In 5 min increments, list the subtasks Kelly does when Kelly is working on the next day's kindergarten lesson plan from 09:00am ~ 12:00pm (total duration in minutes: 180):
1) Kelly is reviewing the kindergarten curriculum standards. (duration in minutes: 15, minutes left: 165)
2) Kelly is brainstorming ideas for the lesson. (duration in minutes: 30, minutes left: 135)
3) Kelly is creating the lesson plan. (duration in minutes: 30, minutes left: 105)
4) Kelly is creating materials for the lesson. (duration in minutes: 30, minutes left: 75)
5) Kelly is taking a break. (duration in minutes: 15, minutes left: 60)
6) Kelly is reviewing the lesson plan. (duration in minutes: 30, minutes left: 30)
7) Kelly is making final changes to the lesson plan. (duration in minutes: 15, minutes left: 15)
8) Kelly is printing the lesson plan. (duration in minutes: 10, minutes left: 5)
9) Kelly is putting the lesson plan in her bag. (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 0)
---
Name: Francisco Lopez
Age: 23
Innate traits: outgoing, friendly, honest
Learned traits: Francisco Lopez is an actor and comedian who loves to entertain others. They are always looking for new ways to make people laugh.
Currently: Francisco Lopez is working on a web series about life in a co-living space. They are also exploring improvisational comedy classes.
Lifestyle: Francisco Lopez goes to bed around 11pm, awakes up around 7am, eats dinner around 6pm.
Daily plan requirement: 
Current Date: Monday February 13

Today is February 13, 2023. From 00:00AM ~ 07:00AM, Francisco Lopez is planning on sleeping, 07:00AM ~ 08:00AM, Francisco Lopez is planning on waking up and completing the morning routine, 08:00AM ~ 12:00PM, Francisco Lopez is planning on working on the web series.
In 5 min increments, list the subtasks Francisco does when Francisco is waking up and completing the morning routine from 07:00AM ~ 08:00AM (total duration in minutes 60): 
1) Francisco is


Output==================================================================
getting out of bed and stretching. (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 55)
2) Francisco is brushing their teeth and washing their face. (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 50)
3) Francisco is getting dressed in their chosen outfit for the day. (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 45)
4) Francisco is making their bed. (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 40)
5) Francisco is preparing and eating breakfast. (duration in minutes: 15, minutes left: 25)
6) Francisco is checking their phone and responding to any urgent messages or emails. (duration in minutes: 10, minutes left: 15)
7) Francisco is packing their bag with any necessary items for the day. (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 10)
8) Francisco is double-checking their schedule for the day. (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 5)
9) Francisco is grabbing their keys and leaving the house to start their day. (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 0)

plan-generate_task_decomp
prompt template : persona/prompt_template/v2/task_decomp_v3.txt
Prompt==================================================================
Describe subtasks in 5 min increments. 
---
Name: Kelly Bronson
Age: 35
Backstory: Kelly always wanted to be a teacher, and now she teaches kindergarten. During the week, she dedicates herself to her students, but on the weekends, she likes to try out new restaurants and hang out with friends. She is very warm and friendly, and loves caring for others.
Personality: sweet, gentle, meticulous
Location: Kelly is in an older condo that has the following areas: {kitchen, bedroom, dining, porch, office, bathroom, living room, hallway}.
Currently: Kelly is a teacher during the school year. She teaches at the school but works on lesson plans at home. She is currently living alone in a single bedroom condo.
Daily plan requirement: Kelly is planning to teach during the morning and work from home in the afternoon.s

Today is Saturday May 10. From 08:00am ~09:00am, Kelly is planning on having breakfast, from 09:00am ~ 12:00pm, Kelly is planning on working on the next day's kindergarten lesson plan, and from 12:00 ~ 13pm, Kelly is planning on taking a break. 
In 5 min increments, list the subtasks Kelly does when Kelly is working on the next day's kindergarten lesson plan from 09:00am ~ 12:00pm (total duration in minutes: 180):
1) Kelly is reviewing the kindergarten curriculum standards. (duration in minutes: 15, minutes left: 165)
2) Kelly is brainstorming ideas for the lesson. (duration in minutes: 30, minutes left: 135)
3) Kelly is creating the lesson plan. (duration in minutes: 30, minutes left: 105)
4) Kelly is creating materials for the lesson. (duration in minutes: 30, minutes left: 75)
5) Kelly is taking a break. (duration in minutes: 15, minutes left: 60)
6) Kelly is reviewing the lesson plan. (duration in minutes: 30, minutes left: 30)
7) Kelly is making final changes to the lesson plan. (duration in minutes: 15, minutes left: 15)
8) Kelly is printing the lesson plan. (duration in minutes: 10, minutes left: 5)
9) Kelly is putting the lesson plan in her bag. (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 0)
---
Name: Hailey Johnson
Age: 30
Innate traits: imaginative, energetic, resourceful
Learned traits: Hailey Johnson is a writer who is always looking for new ways to tell stories. She loves to immerse herself in different cultures and explore their literature.
Currently: Hailey Johnson is writing a novel about a group of artists living in a co-living space. She is also planning to start a podcast.
Lifestyle: Hailey Johnson goes to bed around 2am, awakes up around 10am, eats dinner around 6pm.
Daily plan requirement: 
Current Date: Monday February 13

Today is February 13, 2023. From 00:00AM ~ 10:00AM, Hailey Johnson is planning on sleeping, 10:00AM ~ 11:00AM, Hailey Johnson is planning on waking up and completing her morning routine, 11:00AM ~ 13:00PM, Hailey Johnson is planning on working on her novel.
In 5 min increments, list the subtasks Hailey does when Hailey is waking up and completing her morning routine from 10:00AM ~ 11:00AM (total duration in minutes 60): 
1) Hailey is


Output==================================================================
waking up and stretching. (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 55)
2) Hailey is brushing her teeth and washing her face. (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 50)
3) Hailey is getting dressed for the day. (duration in minutes: 10, minutes left: 40)
4) Hailey is making her bed. (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 35)
5) Hailey is preparing and eating breakfast. (duration in minutes: 20, minutes left: 15)
6) Hailey is packing her bag for the day. (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 10)
7) Hailey is checking her phone and responding to any urgent messages/emails. (duration in minutes: 10, minutes left: 0)


plan-generate_action_sector
prompt template : persona/prompt_template/v1/action_location_sector_v1.txt
Prompt==================================================================
Task -- choose an appropriate area  from the area options for a task at hand. 

Sam Kim lives in {Sam Kim's house} that has Sam Kim's room, bathroom, kitchen.
Sam Kim is currently in {Sam Kim's house} that has Sam Kim's room, bathroom, kitchen. 
Area options: {Sam Kim's house, The Rose and Crown Pub, Hobbs Cafe, Oak Hill College, Johnson Park, Harvey Oak Supply Store, The Willows Market and Pharmacy}.
* Stay in the current area if the activity can be done there. Only go out if the activity needs to take place in another place.
* Must be one of the "Area options," verbatim.
For taking a walk, Sam Kim should go to the following area: {Johnson Park}
---
Jane Anderson lives in {Oak Hill College Student Dormatory} that has Jane Anderson's room.
Jane Anderson is currently in {Oak Hill College} that has a classroom, library
Area options: {Oak Hill College Student Dormatory, The Rose and Crown Pub, Hobbs Cafe, Oak Hill College, Johnson Park, Harvey Oak Supply Store, The Willows Market and Pharmacy}. 
* Stay in the current area if the activity can be done there. Only go out if the activity needs to take place in another place.
* Must be one of the "Area options," verbatim.
For eating dinner, Jane Anderson should go to the following area: {Hobbs Cafe}
---
Hailey Johnson lives in {artist's co-living space} that has Hailey Johnson's room, Hailey Johnson's bathroom, kitchen, common room, Latoya Williams's room, Francisco Lopez's room, Francisco Lopez's bathroom, Rajiv Patel's room.

plan-generate_task_decomp
prompt template : persona/prompt_template/v2/task_decomp_v3.txt
Prompt==================================================================
Describe subtasks in 5 min increments. 
---
Name: Kelly Bronson
Age: 35
Backstory: Kelly always wanted to be a teacher, and now she teaches kindergarten. During the week, she dedicates herself to her students, but on the weekends, she likes to try out new restaurants and hang out with friends. She is very warm and friendly, and loves caring for others.
Personality: sweet, gentle, meticulous
Location: Kelly is in an older condo that has the following areas: {kitchen, bedroom, dining, porch, office, bathroom, living room, hallway}.
Currently: Kelly is a teacher during the school year. She teaches at the school but works on lesson plans at home. She is currently living alone in a single bedroom condo.
Daily plan requirement: Kelly is planning to teach during the morning and work from home in the afternoon.s

Today is Saturday May 10. From 08:00am ~09:00am, Kelly is planning on having breakfast, from 09:00am ~ 12:00pm, Kelly is planning on working on the next day's kindergarten lesson plan, and from 12:00 ~ 13pm, Kelly is planning on taking a break. 
In 5 min increments, list the subtasks Kelly does when Kelly is working on the next day's kindergarten lesson plan from 09:00am ~ 12:00pm (total duration in minutes: 180):
1) Kelly is reviewing the kindergarten curriculum standards. (duration in minutes: 15, minutes left: 165)
2) Kelly is brainstorming ideas for the lesson. (duration in minutes: 30, minutes left: 135)
3) Kelly is creating the lesson plan. (duration in minutes: 30, minutes left: 105)
4) Kelly is creating materials for the lesson. (duration in minutes: 30, minutes left: 75)
5) Kelly is taking a break. (duration in minutes: 15, minutes left: 60)
6) Kelly is reviewing the lesson plan. (duration in minutes: 30, minutes left: 30)
7) Kelly is making final changes to the lesson plan. (duration in minutes: 15, minutes left: 15)
8) Kelly is printing the lesson plan. (duration in minutes: 10, minutes left: 5)
9) Kelly is putting the lesson plan in her bag. (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 0)
---
Name: Arthur Burton
Age: 42
Innate traits: friendly, outgoing, generous
Learned traits: Arthur Burton is a bartender and bar owner of The Rose and Crown Pub who loves to make people feel welcome. He is always looking for ways to make his customers feel special.
Currently: Arthur Burton is running a beloved bar in the town that's been around for 10 years. He is also learning more about mixology and create unique cocktails.
Lifestyle: Arthur Burton goes to bed around midnight, awakes up around 7am, eats dinner around 4pm.
Daily plan requirement: Arthur Burton opens The Rose and Crown Pub at 5pm everyday, and stands at the counter until 10pm, at which point he closes the bar.
Current Date: Monday February 13

Today is February 13, 2023. From 00:00AM ~ 07:00AM, Arthur Burton is planning on sleeping, 07:00AM ~ 08:00AM, Arthur Burton is planning on waking up and completing his morning routine, 08:00AM ~ 09:00AM, Arthur Burton is planning on having breakfast and checking emails.
In 5 min increments, list the subtasks Arthur does when Arthur is waking up and completing his morning routine from 07:00AM ~ 08:00AM (total duration in minutes 60): 
1) Arthur is


Output==================================================================
waking up and stretching. (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 55)
2) Arthur is brushing his teeth. (duration in minutes: 3, minutes left: 52)
3) Arthur is washing his face. (duration in minutes: 2, minutes left: 50)
4) Arthur is combing his hair. (duration in minutes: 2, minutes left: 48)
5) Arthur is getting dressed. (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 43)
6) Arthur is making his bed. (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 38)
7) Arthur is tidying up his bedroom. (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 33)
8) Arthur is preparing his breakfast. (duration in minutes: 10, minutes left: 23)
9) Arthur is setting the table. (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 18)
10) Arthur is eating his breakfast. (duration in minutes: 10, minutes left: 8)
11) Arthur is checking his emails. (duration in minutes: 10, minutes left: -2)

plan-generate_task_decomp
prompt template : persona/prompt_template/v2/task_decomp_v3.txt
Prompt==================================================================
Describe subtasks in 5 min increments. 
---
Name: Kelly Bronson
Age: 35
Backstory: Kelly always wanted to be a teacher, and now she teaches kindergarten. During the week, she dedicates herself to her students, but on the weekends, she likes to try out new restaurants and hang out with friends. She is very warm and friendly, and loves caring for others.
Personality: sweet, gentle, meticulous
Location: Kelly is in an older condo that has the following areas: {kitchen, bedroom, dining, porch, office, bathroom, living room, hallway}.
Currently: Kelly is a teacher during the school year. She teaches at the school but works on lesson plans at home. She is currently living alone in a single bedroom condo.
Daily plan requirement: Kelly is planning to teach during the morning and work from home in the afternoon.s

Today is Saturday May 10. From 08:00am ~09:00am, Kelly is planning on having breakfast, from 09:00am ~ 12:00pm, Kelly is planning on working on the next day's kindergarten lesson plan, and from 12:00 ~ 13pm, Kelly is planning on taking a break. 
In 5 min increments, list the subtasks Kelly does when Kelly is working on the next day's kindergarten lesson plan from 09:00am ~ 12:00pm (total duration in minutes: 180):
1) Kelly is reviewing the kindergarten curriculum standards. (duration in minutes: 15, minutes left: 165)
2) Kelly is brainstorming ideas for the lesson. (duration in minutes: 30, minutes left: 135)
3) Kelly is creating the lesson plan. (duration in minutes: 30, minutes left: 105)
4) Kelly is creating materials for the lesson. (duration in minutes: 30, minutes left: 75)
5) Kelly is taking a break. (duration in minutes: 15, minutes left: 60)
6) Kelly is reviewing the lesson plan. (duration in minutes: 30, minutes left: 30)
7) Kelly is making final changes to the lesson plan. (duration in minutes: 15, minutes left: 15)
8) Kelly is printing the lesson plan. (duration in minutes: 10, minutes left: 5)
9) Kelly is putting the lesson plan in her bag. (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 0)
---
Name: Ryan Park
Age: 29
Innate traits: analytical, pragmatic, driven
Learned traits: Ryan Park is a software engineer who loves to solve problems. He is constantly looking for ways to improve existing systems.
Currently: Ryan Park is working on a project to create a new mobile app. He is also reading up on the latest technologies to stay ahead of the curve.
Lifestyle: Ryan Park goes to bed around 1am, awakes up around 9am, eats dinner around 5pm.
Daily plan requirement: 
Current Date: Monday February 13

Today is February 13, 2023. From 00:00AM ~ 09:00AM, Ryan Park is planning on sleeping, 09:00AM ~ 10:00AM, Ryan Park is planning on waking up and completing the morning routine, 10:00AM ~ 11:00AM, Ryan Park is planning on working on the mobile app project.
In 5 min increments, list the subtasks Ryan does when Ryan is waking up and completing the morning routine from 09:00AM ~ 10:00AM (total duration in minutes 60): 
1) Ryan is


Output==================================================================
getting out of bed. (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 55)
2) Ryan is stretching and doing a quick workout. (duration in minutes: 10, minutes left: 45)
3) Ryan is taking a shower. (duration in minutes: 10, minutes left: 35)
4) Ryan is getting dressed. (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 30)
5) Ryan is brushing his teeth. (duration in minutes: 3, minutes left: 27)
6) Ryan is styling his hair. (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 22)
7) Ryan is making breakfast. (duration in minutes: 15, minutes left: 7)
8) Ryan is eating breakfast. (duration in minutes: 10, minutes left: -3)

prompt template : persona/prompt_template/v2/daily_planning_v6.txt
Prompt==================================================================
Name: Isabella Rodriguez
Age: 34
Innate traits: friendly, outgoing, hospitable
Learned traits: Isabella Rodriguez is a cafe owner of Hobbs Cafe who loves to make people feel welcome. She is always looking for ways to make the cafe a place where people can come to relax and enjoy themselves.
Currently: Isabella Rodriguez is planning on having a Valentine's Day party at Hobbs Cafe with her customers on February 14th, 2023 at 5pm. She is gathering party material, and is telling everyone to join the party at Hobbs Cafe on *February 14th, 2023, from 5pm to 7pm*.
Lifestyle: Isabella Rodriguez goes to bed around 11pm, awakes up around 6am.
Daily plan requirement: Isabella Rodriguez opens Hobbs Cafe at 8am everyday, and stands at the counter until 8pm, at which point she closes the cafe.
Current Date: Monday February 13


In general, Isabella Rodriguez goes to bed around 11pm, awakes up around 6am.
Today is Monday February 13. Here is Isabella's plan today in broad-strokes (with the time of the day. e.g., have a lunch at 12:00 pm, watch TV from 7 to 8 pm): 1) wake up and complete the morning routine at 6:00 am, 2)


Output==================================================================
prepare for the Valentine's Day party at Hobbs Cafe, 3) make a list of party materials and decorations needed, 4) go to the party supply store and purchase the necessary items, 5) return to Hobbs Cafe and set up the decorations, 6) promote the party to customers throughout the day, 7) continue to serve customers and manage the cafe until closing time at 8pm.

prompt template : persona/prompt_template/v2/task_decomp_v3.txt
Prompt==================================================================
Describe subtasks in 5 min increments. 
---
Name: Kelly Bronson
Age: 35
Backstory: Kelly always wanted to be a teacher, and now she teaches kindergarten. During the week, she dedicates herself to her students, but on the weekends, she likes to try out new restaurants and hang out with friends. She is very warm and friendly, and loves caring for others.
Personality: sweet, gentle, meticulous
Location: Kelly is in an older condo that has the following areas: {kitchen, bedroom, dining, porch, office, bathroom, living room, hallway}.
Currently: Kelly is a teacher during the school year. She teaches at the school but works on lesson plans at home. She is currently living alone in a single bedroom condo.
Daily plan requirement: Kelly is planning to teach during the morning and work from home in the afternoon.s

Today is Saturday May 10. From 08:00am ~09:00am, Kelly is planning on having breakfast, from 09:00am ~ 12:00pm, Kelly is planning on working on the next day's kindergarten lesson plan, and from 12:00 ~ 13pm, Kelly is planning on taking a break.

1) Kelly is reviewing the kindergarten curriculum standards. (duration in minutes: 15, minutes left: 165)
2) Kelly is brainstorming ideas for the lesson. (duration in minutes: 30, minutes left: 135)
3) Kelly is creating the lesson plan. (duration in minutes: 30, minutes left: 105)
4) Kelly is creating materials for the lesson. (duration in minutes: 30, minutes left: 75)
5) Kelly is taking a break. (duration in minutes: 15, minutes left: 60)
6) Kelly is reviewing the lesson plan. (duration in minutes: 30, minutes left: 30)
7) Kelly is making final changes to the lesson plan. (duration in minutes: 15, minutes left: 15)
8) Kelly is printing the lesson plan. (duration in minutes: 10, minutes left: 5)
9) Kelly is putting the lesson plan in her bag. (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 0)
---
Name: Isabella Rodriguez
Age: 34
Innate traits: friendly, outgoing, hospitable
Learned traits: Isabella Rodriguez is a cafe owner of Hobbs Cafe who loves to make people feel welcome. She is always looking for ways to make the cafe a place where people can come to relax and enjoy themselves.

5) Isabella is preparing breakfast. (duration in minutes: 15, minutes left: 20)

8) Isabella is gathering her belongings for the day (keys, phone, wallet, etc.). (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 0)

prompt template : persona/prompt_template/v2/task_decomp_v3.txt
Prompt==================================================================
Describe subtasks in 5 min increments. 
---
Name: Kelly Bronson
Age: 35
Backstory: Kelly always wanted to be a teacher, and now she teaches kindergarten. During the week, she dedicates herself to her students, but on the weekends, she likes to try out new restaurants and hang out with friends. She is very warm and friendly, and loves caring for others.
Personality: sweet, gentle, meticulous
Location: Kelly is in an older condo that has the following areas: {kitchen, bedroom, dining, porch, office, bathroom, living room, hallway}.
Currently: Kelly is a teacher during the school year. She teaches at the school but works on lesson plans at home. She is currently living alone in a single bedroom condo.
Daily plan requirement: Kelly is planning to teach during the morning and work from home in the afternoon.s

Today is Saturday May 10. From 08:00am ~09:00am, Kelly is planning on having breakfast, from 09:00am ~ 12:00pm, Kelly is planning on working on the next day's kindergarten lesson plan, and from 12:00 ~ 13pm, Kelly is planning on taking a break. 
In 5 min increments, list the subtasks Kelly does when Kelly is working on the next day's kindergarten lesson plan from 09:00am ~ 12:00pm (total duration in minutes: 180):
1) Kelly is reviewing the kindergarten curriculum standards. (duration in minutes: 15, minutes left: 165)
2) Kelly is brainstorming ideas for the lesson. (duration in minutes: 30, minutes left: 135)
3) Kelly is creating the lesson plan. (duration in minutes: 30, minutes left: 105)
4) Kelly is creating materials for the lesson. (duration in minutes: 30, minutes left: 75)
5) Kelly is taking a break. (duration in minutes: 15, minutes left: 60)
6) Kelly is reviewing the lesson plan. (duration in minutes: 30, minutes left: 30)
7) Kelly is making final changes to the lesson plan. (duration in minutes: 15, minutes left: 15)
8) Kelly is printing the lesson plan. (duration in minutes: 10, minutes left: 5)
9) Kelly is putting the lesson plan in her bag. (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 0)
---
Name: Giorgio Rossi
Age: 41
Innate traits: analytical, logical, eccentric
Learned traits: Giorgio Rossi is a mathematician who loves to solve challenging problems. He is always looking for ways to apply his analytical skills.
Currently: Giorgio Rossi is working on a research project to explore mathematical patterns in nature. He is also taking classes to stay up to date on new mathematical theories. Giorgio is also curious about who will be running for the local mayor election next month and he talks about it a lot with others.
Lifestyle: Giorgio Rossi goes to bed around midnight, awakes up around 7am, eats dinner around 4pm.
Daily plan requirement: 
Current Date: Monday February 13

Today is February 13, 2023. From 00:00AM ~ 07:00AM, Giorgio Rossi is planning on sleeping, 07:00AM ~ 08:00AM, Giorgio Rossi is planning on waking up and completing his morning routine, 08:00AM ~ 09:00AM, Giorgio Rossi is planning on working on his research project.

1) Giorgio is

prompt template : persona/prompt_template/v1/action_location_sector_v1.txt
Prompt==================================================================
Task -- choose an appropriate area  from the area options for a task at hand. 

Sam Kim lives in {Sam Kim's house} that has Sam Kim's room, bathroom, kitchen.
Sam Kim is currently in {Sam Kim's house} that has Sam Kim's room, bathroom, kitchen. 
Area options: {Sam Kim's house, The Rose and Crown Pub, Hobbs Cafe, Oak Hill College, Johnson Park, Harvey Oak Supply Store, The Willows Market and Pharmacy}.
* Stay in the current area if the activity can be done there. Only go out if the activity needs to take place in another place.
* Must be one of the "Area options," verbatim.
For taking a walk, Sam Kim should go to the following area: {Johnson Park}
---
Jane Anderson lives in {Oak Hill College Student Dormatory} that has Jane Anderson's room.

prompt template : persona/prompt_template/v2/task_decomp_v3.txt
Prompt==================================================================
Describe subtasks in 5 min increments. 
---
Name: Kelly Bronson
Age: 35
Backstory: Kelly always wanted to be a teacher, and now she teaches kindergarten. During the week, she dedicates herself to her students, but on the weekends, she likes to try out new restaurants and hang out with friends. She is very warm and friendly, and loves caring for others.
Personality: sweet, gentle, meticulous
Location: Kelly is in an older condo that has the following areas: {kitchen, bedroom, dining, porch, office, bathroom, living room, hallway}.
Currently: Kelly is a teacher during the school year. She teaches at the school but works on lesson plans at home. She is currently living alone in a single bedroom condo.
Daily plan requirement: Kelly is planning to teach during the morning and work from home in the afternoon.s

Today is Saturday May 10. From 08:00am ~09:00am, Kelly is planning on having breakfast, from 09:00am ~ 12:00pm, Kelly is planning on working on the next day's kindergarten lesson plan, and from 12:00 ~ 13pm, Kelly is planning on taking a break. 
In 5 min increments, list the subtasks Kelly does when Kelly is working on the next day's kindergarten lesson plan from 09:00am ~ 12:00pm (total duration in minutes: 180):
1) Kelly is reviewing the kindergarten curriculum standards. (duration in minutes: 15, minutes left: 165)
2) Kelly is brainstorming ideas for the lesson. (duration in minutes: 30, minutes left: 135)
3) Kelly is creating the lesson plan. (duration in minutes: 30, minutes left: 105)
4) Kelly is creating materials for the lesson. (duration in minutes: 30, minutes left: 75)
5) Kelly is taking a break. (duration in minutes: 15, minutes left: 60)
6) Kelly is reviewing the lesson plan. (duration in minutes: 30, minutes left: 30)
7) Kelly is making final changes to the lesson plan. (duration in minutes: 15, minutes left: 15)
8) Kelly is printing the lesson plan. (duration in minutes: 10, minutes left: 5)
9) Kelly is putting the lesson plan in her bag. (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 0)
---
Name: Carlos Gomez
Age: 32
Innate traits: loud, rude, toxic
Learned traits: Carlos Gomez is a poet who loves to explore his inner thoughts and feelings. He is always looking for new ways to express himself.
Currently: Carlos Gomez is working on a collection of poetry that explores the beauty of the natural world. He is also attending creative writing workshops to hone his skills.

Current Date: Monday February 13

Today is February 13, 2023. From 00:00AM ~ 07:00AM, Carlos Gomez is planning on sleeping, 07:00AM ~ 08:00AM, Carlos Gomez is planning on waking up and completing his morning routine, 08:00AM ~ 12:00PM, Carlos Gomez is planning on attending a creative writing workshop.

1) Carlos is


Output==================================================================
waking up and stretching. (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 55)
2) Carlos is brushing his teeth. (duration in minutes: 3, minutes left: 52)
3) Carlos is washing his face. (duration in minutes: 2, minutes left: 50)
4) Carlos is getting dressed. (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 45)
5) Carlos is making his bed. (duration in minutes: 2, minutes left: 43)
6) Carlos is having breakfast. (duration in minutes: 10, minutes left: 33)
7) Carlos is packing his bag for the workshop. (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 28)
8) Carlos is checking his schedule and making sure he has everything he needs. (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 23)
9) Carlos is leaving his home and locking the door. (duration in minutes: 2, minutes left: 21)

plan-_determine_action
plan-generate_task_decomp
prompt template : persona/prompt_template/v2/task_decomp_v3.txt
Prompt==================================================================
Describe subtasks in 5 min increments. 
---
Name: Kelly Bronson
Age: 35
Backstory: Kelly always wanted to be a teacher, and now she teaches kindergarten. During the week, she dedicates herself to her students, but on the weekends, she likes to try out new restaurants and hang out with friends. She is very warm and friendly, and loves caring for others.
Personality: sweet, gentle, meticulous
Location: Kelly is in an older condo that has the following areas: {kitchen, bedroom, dining, porch, office, bathroom, living room, hallway}.
Currently: Kelly is a teacher during the school year. She teaches at the school but works on lesson plans at home. She is currently living alone in a single bedroom condo.
Daily plan requirement: Kelly is planning to teach during the morning and work from home in the afternoon.s

Today is Saturday May 10. From 08:00am ~09:00am, Kelly is planning on having breakfast, from 09:00am ~ 12:00pm, Kelly is planning on working on the next day's kindergarten lesson plan, and from 12:00 ~ 13pm, Kelly is planning on taking a break. 
In 5 min increments, list the subtasks Kelly does when Kelly is working on the next day's kindergarten lesson plan from 09:00am ~ 12:00pm (total duration in minutes: 180):
1) Kelly is reviewing the kindergarten curriculum standards. (duration in minutes: 15, minutes left: 165)

plan-generate_task_decomp
prompt template : persona/prompt_template/v2/task_decomp_v3.txt
Prompt==================================================================
Describe subtasks in 5 min increments. 
---
Name: Kelly Bronson
Age: 35
Backstory: Kelly always wanted to be a teacher, and now she teaches kindergarten. During the week, she dedicates herself to her students, but on the weekends, she likes to try out new restaurants and hang out with friends. She is very warm and friendly, and loves caring for others.
Personality: sweet, gentle, meticulous
Location: Kelly is in an older condo that has the following areas: {kitchen, bedroom, dining, porch, office, bathroom, living room, hallway}.
Currently: Kelly is a teacher during the school year. She teaches at the school but works on lesson plans at home. She is currently living alone in a single bedroom condo.
Daily plan requirement: Kelly is planning to teach during the morning and work from home in the afternoon.s

Today is Saturday May 10. From 08:00am ~09:00am, Kelly is planning on having breakfast, from 09:00am ~ 12:00pm, Kelly is planning on working on the next day's kindergarten lesson plan, and from 12:00 ~ 13pm, Kelly is planning on taking a break. 
In 5 min increments, list the subtasks Kelly does when Kelly is working on the next day's kindergarten lesson plan from 09:00am ~ 12:00pm (total duration in minutes: 180):

5) Kelly is taking a break. (duration in minutes: 15, minutes left: 60)

---

plan-generate_task_decomp
prompt template : persona/prompt_template/v2/task_decomp_v3.txt
Prompt==================================================================
Describe subtasks in 5 min increments. 
---
Name: Kelly Bronson
Age: 35
Backstory: Kelly always wanted to be a teacher, and now she teaches kindergarten. During the week, she dedicates herself to her students, but on the weekends, she likes to try out new restaurants and hang out with friends. She is very warm and friendly, and loves caring for others.
Personality: sweet, gentle, meticulous
Location: Kelly is in an older condo that has the following areas: {kitchen, bedroom, dining, porch, office, bathroom, living room, hallway}.
Currently: Kelly is a teacher during the school year. She teaches at the school but works on lesson plans at home. She is currently living alone in a single bedroom condo.
Daily plan requirement: Kelly is planning to teach during the morning and work from home in the afternoon.s

Today is Saturday May 10. From 08:00am ~09:00am, Kelly is planning on having breakfast, from 09:00am ~ 12:00pm, Kelly is planning on working on the next day's kindergarten lesson plan, and from 12:00 ~ 13pm, Kelly is planning on taking a break. 
In 5 min increments, list the subtasks Kelly does when Kelly is working on the next day's kindergarten lesson plan from 09:00am ~ 12:00pm (total duration in minutes: 180):
1) Kelly is reviewing the kindergarten curriculum standards. (duration in minutes: 15, minutes left: 165)
2) Kelly is brainstorming ideas for the lesson. (duration in minutes: 30, minutes left: 135)
3) Kelly is creating the lesson plan. (duration in minutes: 30, minutes left: 105)
4) Kelly is creating materials for the lesson. (duration in minutes: 30, minutes left: 75)
5) Kelly is taking a break. (duration in minutes: 15, minutes left: 60)
6) Kelly is reviewing the lesson plan. (duration in minutes: 30, minutes left: 30)
7) Kelly is making final changes to the lesson plan. (duration in minutes: 15, minutes left: 15)
8) Kelly is printing the lesson plan. (duration in minutes: 10, minutes left: 5)
9) Kelly is putting the lesson plan in her bag. (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 0)
---
Name: Ayesha Khan
Age: 20
Innate traits: curious, determined, independent
Learned traits: Ayesha Khan is a college student who loves to explore literature. She is curious and determined to understand the nuances of each work.
Currently: Ayesha Khan is researching for her senior thesis on the use of language in Shakespeare’s plays. She is also taking classes to learn more about writing.
Lifestyle: Ayesha Khan goes to bed around 10pm, awakes up around 6am, eats dinner around 5pm.
Daily plan requirement: Ayesha Khan goes to the library at Oak Hill College to take classes from 10am to 2pm, and then spends her days studying at the library.
Current Date: Monday February 13

Today is February 13, 2023. From 00:00AM ~ 06:00AM, Ayesha Khan is planning on sleeping, 06:00AM ~ 07:00AM, Ayesha Khan is planning on waking up and completing her morning routine, 07:00AM ~ 08:00AM, Ayesha Khan is planning on having breakfast.
In 5 min increments, list the subtasks Ayesha does when Ayesha is waking up and completing her morning routine from 06:00AM ~ 07:00AM (total duration in minutes 60): 
1) Ayesha is


Output==================================================================
waking up and turning off her alarm. (duration in minutes: 1, minutes left: 59)
2) Ayesha is stretching and doing some light exercises. (duration in minutes: 10, minutes left: 49)
3) Ayesha is taking a shower and getting dressed. (duration in minutes: 15, minutes left: 34)
4) Ayesha is brushing her teeth and washing her face. (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 29)
5) Ayesha is making her bed. (duration in minutes: 3, minutes left: 26)
6) Ayesha is tidying up her room. (duration in minutes: 10, minutes left: 16)
7) Ayesha is preparing breakfast. (duration in minutes: 10, minutes left: 6)
8) Ayesha is eating breakfast. (duration in minutes: 6, minutes left: 0)

Name: Wolfgang Schulz
Age: 21

Learned traits: Wolfgang Schulz is a student at Oak Hill College studying chemistry and a student athlete. He is very dedicated to both his academics and his sport.
Currently: Wolfgang Schulz is training for his next competition and studying for his exams. He is also looking for ways to make his studies more efficient.
Lifestyle: Wolfgang Schulz goes to bed around 9pm, awakes up around 5am, eats dinner around 6pm.

Current Date: Monday February 13


In general, Wolfgang Schulz goes to bed around 9pm, awakes up around 5am, eats dinner around 6pm.
Today is Monday February 13. Here is Wolfgang's plan today in broad-strokes (with the time of the day. e.g., have a lunch at 12:00 pm, watch TV from 7 to 8 pm): 1) wake up and complete the morning routine at 5:00 am, 2)


Output==================================================================
go for a run at the park at 6:00 am, 3) return home and have breakfast at 7:00 am, 4) start studying for exams at 8:00 am, 5) take a break for lunch at 12:00 pm, 6) resume studying at 1:00 pm, 7) take another break for a light snack at 3:00 pm, 8) continue studying until 5:00 pm, 9) start exercising in his room at 6:00 pm, 10) have dinner at 7:00 pm, 11) review material and make study notes from 8:00 pm to 9:00 pm, 12) wind down and relax before going to bed at 9:00 pm.

plan-generate_task_decomp
prompt template : persona/prompt_template/v2/task_decomp_v3.txt
Prompt==================================================================
Describe subtasks in 5 min increments. 
---
Name: Kelly Bronson
Age: 35
Backstory: Kelly always wanted to be a teacher, and now she teaches kindergarten. During the week, she dedicates herself to her students, but on the weekends, she likes to try out new restaurants and hang out with friends. She is very warm and friendly, and loves caring for others.
Personality: sweet, gentle, meticulous
Location: Kelly is in an older condo that has the following areas: {kitchen, bedroom, dining, porch, office, bathroom, living room, hallway}.
Currently: Kelly is a teacher during the school year. She teaches at the school but works on lesson plans at home. She is currently living alone in a single bedroom condo.
Daily plan requirement: Kelly is planning to teach during the morning and work from home in the afternoon.s

Today is Saturday May 10. From 08:00am ~09:00am, Kelly is planning on having breakfast, from 09:00am ~ 12:00pm, Kelly is planning on working on the next day's kindergarten lesson plan, and from 12:00 ~ 13pm, Kelly is planning on taking a break. 
In 5 min increments, list the subtasks Kelly does when Kelly is working on the next day's kindergarten lesson plan from 09:00am ~ 12:00pm (total duration in minutes: 180):
1) Kelly is reviewing the kindergarten curriculum standards. (duration in minutes: 15, minutes left: 165)
2) Kelly is brainstorming ideas for the lesson. (duration in minutes: 30, minutes left: 135)
3) Kelly is creating the lesson plan. (duration in minutes: 30, minutes left: 105)
4) Kelly is creating materials for the lesson. (duration in minutes: 30, minutes left: 75)
5) Kelly is taking a break. (duration in minutes: 15, minutes left: 60)
6) Kelly is reviewing the lesson plan. (duration in minutes: 30, minutes left: 30)
7) Kelly is making final changes to the lesson plan. (duration in minutes: 15, minutes left: 15)
8) Kelly is printing the lesson plan. (duration in minutes: 10, minutes left: 5)
9) Kelly is putting the lesson plan in her bag. (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 0)
---
Name: Wolfgang Schulz
Age: 21
Innate traits: Hardworking, passionate, dedicated
Learned traits: Wolfgang Schulz is a student at Oak Hill College studying chemistry and a student athlete. He is very dedicated to both his academics and his sport.
Currently: Wolfgang Schulz is training for his next competition and studying for his exams. He is also looking for ways to make his studies more efficient.
Lifestyle: Wolfgang Schulz goes to bed around 9pm, awakes up around 5am, eats dinner around 6pm.
Daily plan requirement: Wolfgang Schulz goes for a run at the part in the morning, studies during the day, and exercises at his room at night 
Current Date: Monday February 13

Today is February 13, 2023. From 00:00AM ~ 05:00AM, Wolfgang Schulz is planning on sleeping, 05:00AM ~ 06:00AM, Wolfgang Schulz is planning on completing his morning routine, 06:00AM ~ 07:00AM, Wolfgang Schulz is planning on going for a run at the park.
In 5 min increments, list the subtasks Wolfgang does when Wolfgang is completing his morning routine from 05:00AM ~ 06:00AM (total duration in minutes 60): 
1) Wolfgang is


Output==================================================================
waking up and getting out of bed. (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 55)
2) Wolfgang is stretching and doing light exercises to wake up his body. (duration in minutes: 10, minutes left: 45)
3) Wolfgang is washing his face and brushing his teeth. (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 40)
4) Wolfgang is getting dressed in his running clothes. (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 35)
5) Wolfgang is preparing a quick breakfast, such as a banana and a protein shake. (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 30)
6) Wolfgang is checking his phone for any important messages or notifications. (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 25)
7) Wolfgang is gathering his running essentials, such as his running shoes, water bottle, and headphones. (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 20)
8) Wolfgang is doing a quick warm-up routine to prepare his body for the run. (duration in minutes: 10, minutes left: 10)
9) Wolfgang is planning his running route and setting a goal for the run. (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 5)
10) Wolfgang is stepping out the door and starting his run. (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 0)

Output==================================================================

plan-_determine_action
plan-generate_task_decomp
prompt template : persona/prompt_template/v2/task_decomp_v3.txt
Prompt==================================================================
Describe subtasks in 5 min increments. 
---
Name: Kelly Bronson
Age: 35
Backstory: Kelly always wanted to be a teacher, and now she teaches kindergarten. During the week, she dedicates herself to her students, but on the weekends, she likes to try out new restaurants and hang out with friends. She is very warm and friendly, and loves caring for others.
Personality: sweet, gentle, meticulous
Location: Kelly is in an older condo that has the following areas: {kitchen, bedroom, dining, porch, office, bathroom, living room, hallway}.
Currently: Kelly is a teacher during the school year. She teaches at the school but works on lesson plans at home. She is currently living alone in a single bedroom condo.
Daily plan requirement: Kelly is planning to teach during the morning and work from home in the afternoon.s

Today is Saturday May 10. From 08:00am ~09:00am, Kelly is planning on having breakfast, from 09:00am ~ 12:00pm, Kelly is planning on working on the next day's kindergarten lesson plan, and from 12:00 ~ 13pm, Kelly is planning on taking a break. 
In 5 min increments, list the subtasks Kelly does when Kelly is working on the next day's kindergarten lesson plan from 09:00am ~ 12:00pm (total duration in minutes: 180):
1) Kelly is reviewing the kindergarten curriculum standards. (duration in minutes: 15, minutes left: 165)
2) Kelly is brainstorming ideas for the lesson. (duration in minutes: 30, minutes left: 135)
3) Kelly is creating the lesson plan. (duration in minutes: 30, minutes left: 105)
4) Kelly is creating materials for the lesson. (duration in minutes: 30, minutes left: 75)

Age: 44

Currently: Mei Lin is living with her husband, John Lin, and son, Eddy Lin, and is teaching a course on philosophy and working on her research paper. She also is helping her two kids with their schoolwork.

===
Name: John Lin
Age: 45
Innate traits: patient, kind, organized
Learned traits: John Lin is a pharmacy shop keeper at the Willow Market and Pharmacy who loves to help people. He is always looking for ways to make the process of getting medication easier for his customers.
Currently: John Lin is living with his wife, Mei Lin, and son, Eddy Lin, and is shop keeping a pharmacy at the Willow Market and Pharmacy. He is also taking online classes to stay up to date on new medications and treatments. John is also curious about who will be running for the local mayor election next month and he is asking everyone he meets about who will be running in the election.
Lifestyle: John Lin goes to bed around 10pm, awakes up around 6am, eats dinner around 5pm.
Daily plan requirement: John Lin goes to the Willow Market and Pharmacy around 9am to open the pharmacy counter. He stands behind the counter until 5pm and returns home.
Current Date: Monday February 13

prompt template : persona/prompt_template/v2/task_decomp_v3.txt
Prompt==================================================================
Describe subtasks in 5 min increments. 
---
Name: Kelly Bronson
Age: 35
Backstory: Kelly always wanted to be a teacher, and now she teaches kindergarten. During the week, she dedicates herself to her students, but on the weekends, she likes to try out new restaurants and hang out with friends. She is very warm and friendly, and loves caring for others.
Personality: sweet, gentle, meticulous
Location: Kelly is in an older condo that has the following areas: {kitchen, bedroom, dining, porch, office, bathroom, living room, hallway}.
Currently: Kelly is a teacher during the school year. She teaches at the school but works on lesson plans at home. She is currently living alone in a single bedroom condo.
Daily plan requirement: Kelly is planning to teach during the morning and work from home in the afternoon.s

Today is Saturday May 10. From 08:00am ~09:00am, Kelly is planning on having breakfast, from 09:00am ~ 12:00pm, Kelly is planning on working on the next day's kindergarten lesson plan, and from 12:00 ~ 13pm, Kelly is planning on taking a break. 
In 5 min increments, list the subtasks Kelly does when Kelly is working on the next day's kindergarten lesson plan from 09:00am ~ 12:00pm (total duration in minutes: 180):
1) Kelly is reviewing the kindergarten curriculum standards. (duration in minutes: 15, minutes left: 165)
2) Kelly is brainstorming ideas for the lesson. (duration in minutes: 30, minutes left: 135)
3) Kelly is creating the lesson plan. (duration in minutes: 30, minutes left: 105)
4) Kelly is creating materials for the lesson. (duration in minutes: 30, minutes left: 75)
5) Kelly is taking a break. (duration in minutes: 15, minutes left: 60)
6) Kelly is reviewing the lesson plan. (duration in minutes: 30, minutes left: 30)
7) Kelly is making final changes to the lesson plan. (duration in minutes: 15, minutes left: 15)
8) Kelly is printing the lesson plan. (duration in minutes: 10, minutes left: 5)
9) Kelly is putting the lesson plan in her bag. (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 0)
---
Name: John Lin
Age: 45
Innate traits: patient, kind, organized
Learned traits: John Lin is a pharmacy shop keeper at the Willow Market and Pharmacy who loves to help people. He is always looking for ways to make the process of getting medication easier for his customers.
Currently: John Lin is living with his wife, Mei Lin, and son, Eddy Lin, and is shop keeping a pharmacy at the Willow Market and Pharmacy. He is also taking online classes to stay up to date on new medications and treatments. John is also curious about who will be running for the local mayor election next month and he is asking everyone he meets about who will be running in the election.
Lifestyle: John Lin goes to bed around 10pm, awakes up around 6am, eats dinner around 5pm.
Daily plan requirement: John Lin goes to the Willow Market and Pharmacy around 9am to open the pharmacy counter. He stands behind the counter until 5pm and returns home.
Current Date: Monday February 13

Today is February 13, 2023. From 00:00AM ~ 06:00AM, John Lin is planning on sleeping, 06:00AM ~ 07:00AM, John Lin is planning on waking up and completing his morning routine, 07:00AM ~ 08:00AM, John Lin is planning on eating breakfast.

1) John is

4) John is getting dressed. (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 40) 
5) John is combing his hair. (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 35) 
6) John is checking his phone for any important messages or notifications. (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 30) 
7) John is drinking a glass of water. (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 25)

9) John is eating breakfast. (duration in minutes: 15, minutes left: 0)


plan-generate_action_sector
prompt template : persona/prompt_template/v1/action_location_sector_v1.txt
Prompt==================================================================
Task -- choose an appropriate area  from the area options for a task at hand. 

Sam Kim lives in {Sam Kim's house} that has Sam Kim's room, bathroom, kitchen.
Sam Kim is currently in {Sam Kim's house} that has Sam Kim's room, bathroom, kitchen. 
Area options: {Sam Kim's house, The Rose and Crown Pub, Hobbs Cafe, Oak Hill College, Johnson Park, Harvey Oak Supply Store, The Willows Market and Pharmacy}.
* Stay in the current area if the activity can be done there. Only go out if the activity needs to take place in another place.
* Must be one of the "Area options," verbatim.
For taking a walk, Sam Kim should go to the following area: {Johnson Park}
---

plan-generate_task_decomp
prompt template : persona/prompt_template/v2/task_decomp_v3.txt
Prompt==================================================================
Describe subtasks in 5 min increments. 
---
Name: Kelly Bronson
Age: 35
Backstory: Kelly always wanted to be a teacher, and now she teaches kindergarten. During the week, she dedicates herself to her students, but on the weekends, she likes to try out new restaurants and hang out with friends. She is very warm and friendly, and loves caring for others.
Personality: sweet, gentle, meticulous
Location: Kelly is in an older condo that has the following areas: {kitchen, bedroom, dining, porch, office, bathroom, living room, hallway}.
Currently: Kelly is a teacher during the school year. She teaches at the school but works on lesson plans at home. She is currently living alone in a single bedroom condo.
Daily plan requirement: Kelly is planning to teach during the morning and work from home in the afternoon.s

Today is Saturday May 10. From 08:00am ~09:00am, Kelly is planning on having breakfast, from 09:00am ~ 12:00pm, Kelly is planning on working on the next day's kindergarten lesson plan, and from 12:00 ~ 13pm, Kelly is planning on taking a break. 
In 5 min increments, list the subtasks Kelly does when Kelly is working on the next day's kindergarten lesson plan from 09:00am ~ 12:00pm (total duration in minutes: 180):
1) Kelly is reviewing the kindergarten curriculum standards. (duration in minutes: 15, minutes left: 165)
2) Kelly is brainstorming ideas for the lesson. (duration in minutes: 30, minutes left: 135)
3) Kelly is creating the lesson plan. (duration in minutes: 30, minutes left: 105)
4) Kelly is creating materials for the lesson. (duration in minutes: 30, minutes left: 75)
5) Kelly is taking a break. (duration in minutes: 15, minutes left: 60)
6) Kelly is reviewing the lesson plan. (duration in minutes: 30, minutes left: 30)
7) Kelly is making final changes to the lesson plan. (duration in minutes: 15, minutes left: 15)
8) Kelly is printing the lesson plan. (duration in minutes: 10, minutes left: 5)
9) Kelly is putting the lesson plan in her bag. (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 0)
---
Name: Eddy Lin
Age: 19
Innate traits: curious, analytical, musical
Learned traits: Eddy Lin is a student at Oak Hill College studying music theory and composition. He loves to explore different musical styles and is always looking for ways to expand his knowledge.
Currently: Eddy Lin is working on a composition project for his college class. He is also taking classes to learn more about music theory.
Lifestyle: Eddy Lin goes to bed around 11pm, awakes up around 7amam, eats dinner around 5pm.
Daily plan requirement: Eddy Lin goes to Oak Hill College to take classes starting 10am. In the afternoon, he likes to go to Hobbs Cafe to eat and study.
Current Date: Monday February 13

Today is February 13, 2023. From 00:00AM ~ 07:00AM, Eddy Lin is planning on sleeping, 07:00AM ~ 08:00AM, Eddy Lin is planning on waking up and completing the morning routine, 08:00AM ~ 12:00PM, Eddy Lin is planning on attending classes at Oak Hill College.
In 5 min increments, list the subtasks Eddy does when Eddy is waking up and completing the morning routine from 07:00AM ~ 08:00AM (total duration in minutes 60): 
1) Eddy is


Output==================================================================
waking up and stretching (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 55)
2) Eddy is brushing his teeth (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 50)
3) Eddy is washing his face (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 45)
4) Eddy is getting dressed (duration in minutes: 10, minutes left: 35)
5) Eddy is making his bed (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 30)
6) Eddy is preparing breakfast (duration in minutes: 10, minutes left: 20)
7) Eddy is eating breakfast (duration in minutes: 10, minutes left: 10)
8) Eddy is packing his bag with his college materials (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 5)
9) Eddy is checking his schedule and organizing his day (duration in minutes: 5, minutes left: 0)
